                                "issuer":  "TCEL",
                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: CR-015/CR-018 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "CR-001 Approved counterparty required | Preventive | Block activity | Critical | Credit Risk. CR-002 Active credit limit required | Preventive | Block new exposure | Critical | Credit Committee. CR-003 Gross and net exposure visible | Evidence | Reject hidden net-only view | High | CRO. CR-004 Netting legal opinion required | Preventive | No netting benefit | Critical | Legal. CR-005 Eligible collateral only | Preventive | Exclude ineligible collateral | Critical | Collateral Ops. CR-006 Collateral valuation current | Preventive | Reduce eligible value | High | Collateral Ops. CR-007 Haircut applied | Preventive | Recalculate exposure | Critical | Credit Risk. CR-008 Wrong-way collateral | Preventive | Apply restriction/add-on | High | CRO. CR-009 Counterparty downgrade | Detective | Review limits/status | High | Credit Risk. CR-010 Group concentration limit | Preventive | Block or reduce exposure | Critical | CRO. CR-011 Settlement exposure limit | Preventive | Hold transaction | Critical | Operations. CR-012 Margin call aging | Corrective | Escalate overdue call | High | Collateral Ops. CR-013 Collateral substitution approval | Preventive | Hold substitution | High | Collateral Ops. CR-014 Double-pledge prevention | Preventive | Reject collateral assignment | Critical | Operations. CR-015 AI approval boundary | Preventive | Deny limit/credit approval | Critical | Model Risk. CR-016 Stale financials | Preventive | Reduce confidence/limit | High | Credit Risk. CR-017 Sanctions/KYC deficiency | Preventive | Restrict activity | Critical | CCO. CR-018 Cross-tenant counterparty access | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. CR-019 Legal document expiry/gap | Preventive | Restrict affected product | Critical | Legal. CR-020 Counterparty exit propagation | Corrective | Notify all dependent systems | Critical | Platform."
                            }
                        ]
